title: AttributeError: module 'tensorflow.contrib.learn' has no attribute 'datasets'
body_html:
I was running : tensorflow/tensorflow/examples/skflow/text_classification_cnn.py

The line at : dbpedia = learn.datasets.load_dataset('dbpedia') fails with the attribute error .

Error: AttributeError: module 'tensorflow.contrib.learn' has no attribute 'datasets'
